      {
        "step_no": 1,
        "text": "Prepare meatball mixture by combining ground turkey, crumbled feta, beaten egg, minced garlic, grated and squeezed onion, chopped parsley, dried oregano, salt and pepper in a large bowl; mix gently until just combined.",
